</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-19">This relation is read as "position of COM is mass weighted average of the positions of particles". 
</para>
<para id="element-20">Further, COM is a geometric point in three-dimensional volume and it involves distribution of mass with respect to some reference system. This expression of the position of COM is description of a position in three dimensional volume. Now, substituting with appropriate symbols, we have :
</para>
<para id="element-21">
<m:math display="block">
