</para>
<para id="element-25">We know that there are only two directions involved with each of the axes. As such, we assign positive value for distances in reference direction and negative in opposite direction. 
</para>

<section id="section-1a">
<title> Special cases  </title>
<para id="element-26"><term>(a)</term> Particle system along a straight line :
</para>
<para id="element-27">COM of particle system along a straight line is given by the scalar expression in one dimension:
</para>
<para id="element-28">
