<section id="section-2">
<title> COM of rigid body </title>
<para id="element-54">Rigid body is composed of very large numbers of particles. Mass of rigid body is distributed closely. Thus, the distribution of mass can be treated as continuous. The mathematical expression for rigid body, therefore, is modified involving integration. The integral expressions of the components of position of COM in three mutually perpendicular directions are : 

</para>
